Starting with a conversation between Enrique Walker and the Dutch architect Neutelings Riedijk, and an introduction by Aaron Betsky, this issue of El Croquis presents the buildings and projects executed in the last nine years by the bureau.

Featured are, among others, the Institute for Sound and Vision in Hilversum, the Museum aan de Stroom MAS in Antwerp and the Sphinxes Lakeshore Housing
